metadata.name: Heart's Path
metadata.description:
A heart's path is linear. The life of a heart includes a beginning, middle, and an end. The heart endures monotony with aplomb. However, monotony seldom endures long term. The heart must needs to endure storms, darkness, pains, burdens, suffering, exaltation, excitement, joy, happiness, sadness, grief, and depression. These are but a few of the trials and tribulations which break the monotony of life.

The journey of a heart envisioned.
